										<footer class="article-contributor contributors">
									

<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>James Lainsbury</strong></span> has worked as a logger, editor, and many things in between. He is a Mainer by birth but is currently nestled between Interstate 90 and the rail yard in Missoula, Montana, with his girlfriend and a moody springer spaniel. His essay &ldquo;Control&rdquo; is part of a larger, unpublished work.</p><a href="/contributors/james-lainsbury" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

